## Components
1. XTransfer：Transfer A to B
2. XFront: Pre-processing
3. XRear: Post-processing
4. XBridge:
    * (FreeRTOS/Arduino/ESP-IDF) Queue
    * (ESP-IDF) MQTT, UART, ...
    * (Linux) Unix Domain/Queue/FIFO， TCP/UDP, tty, ...

